                <h3 id="ons-typefaces">Type styles</h3>
                <p>We've developed a set of typography styles that can be applied to documents showcasing how we intend to build hierarchy and recognition. Our styles are intended to create impactful, informative statements and content that's easy to skim.</p>
                <p>Working best on white background, our type styles are designed for use on standard A4 text-heavy materials such as reports, letters and handbooks. When you need to use a coloured background, it is recommended that text should be white.</p>
